org.mapfish.print.attribute

Class ArrayReflectiveAttribute<Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapfish.print.attribute.ArrayReflectiveAttribute<Value>
  • Type Parameters:
    Value - the type of each element in the array
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Attribute, ConfigurationObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TableListAttribute

    public abstract class ArrayReflectiveAttribute<Value>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Attribute
    An attribute which is essentially a ReflectiveAttribute but rather than representing a single object it represents an array of objects.
